benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: DELETE /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/tags - Remove tags from bundle

covered: Valid Deletion: Scenarios cover successful deletion of tags from bundles.
Non-Existent Resource: Scenarios handle attempts to delete tags from non-existent bundles.

gaps: Concurrency: No tests cover race conditions when multiple users attempt to delete tags simultaneously.

recommendations: Add tests for concurrency to ensure proper handling of simultaneous DELETE requests.
